@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@submissionId = 1

### ==========================================
### Submission Upload — ATTACHMENT
### ==========================================

### Step 1: Request Upload URL
# @name requestUploadAttachment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/files/submission/{{submissionId}}/request-upload HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "originalName": "test-document.pdf",
    "mimeType": "application/pdf",
    "submissionFileType": "ATTACHMENT"
}


### Step 2: Upload file directly to Azure
PUT {{requestUploadAttachment.response.body.uploadUrl}} HTTP/1.1
x-ms-blob-type: BlockBlob
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test-files/test-document.pdf


### Step 3: Confirm Upload
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/files/submission/{{submissionId}}/confirm-upload HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "uuid": "{{requestUploadAttachment.response.body.uuid}}",
    "originalName": "test-document.pdf",
    "submissionFileType": "ATTACHMENT"
}


