### ==========================================
### Query
### ==========================================

### Get Files - Submission (all active)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/submission/{{submissionId}} HTTP/1.1


### Get Files - Submission (filter by status)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/submission/{{submissionId}}?status=ACTIVE HTTP/1.1


### Get Files - Submission (filter by attachment type)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/submission/{{submissionId}}?submissionFileType=ATTACHMENT HTTP/1.1


### Get Files - Submission (filter by recognition type)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/submission/{{submissionId}}?submissionFileType=RECOGNITION HTTP/1.1


### ==========================================
### File Access
### ==========================================

### Preview File (replace UUID with actual value)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/preview HTTP/1.1


### Download File (replace UUID with actual value)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/download HTTP/1.1


### Delete File (replace UUID with actual value)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/files/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000 HTTP/1.1
